 *  *************************************************************************
 *  @brief:       Connect to WiFi using ESP32
 *  @note:
 *  *************************************************************************
 *  @param[in]:   char ssid []
 *                char password []
 *  @param[out]:   
 *  @return:      [true]  = wifi connection is established
 *                [false] = wifi connection failed
